{"title":"大巴山月","authors":["梁上泉"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":10,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大巴山月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁上泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮，月亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂在大巴山上；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山上，山上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少眼睛张望！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山月白如雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山月明如霜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人在清辉里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似闻月桂香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香绕苏区三千里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾随战歌远飞荡——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照到营帐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士都枕戈待旦；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照到路口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪动着旗影刀光；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照到竹林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青年忙做红缨枪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照到巴河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姐妹争洗红军装……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无数次缺了又圆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无数次暗了又亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又是一样的银夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍是同样的月光！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再照老营，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"?兽的木梆阵阵响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再照路口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩门顶上马蹄高扬；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再照竹林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁作横笛试新声；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再照巴河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两岸情歌风传唱……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昂头屹立的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼里总有个月亮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮也开笑眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把大巴山久久凝望。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}